howard also voiced roo in disney 's animated shorts winnie the pooh and the honey tree ( 1966 ) and winnie the pooh and the blustery day ( 1968 ) , which were later incorporated into the many adventures of winnie the pooh ( 1977 ) , and hathi 's son hathi jr. in the jungle book ( 1967 ) .

